INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("27", "5", "2015-04-15 20:23:41", "2015-04-15 20:23:41", "\n    Wine\n    Champagne\n    Spirits\n    Liqueurs\n    Beer\n    Mixers\n    Barware\n    Gifts\n    What\'s New\n    OUR BLOG\n\n    Free Delivery over £100\n\n    Excellent 9.5/10\n\n    Gifts delivered next day\n\n    Home /\n    Moët & Chandon Brut Impérial Champagne\n\nMoët & Chandon\nMoët & Chandon Brut Impérial Champagne\nIconic Champagne\n\n    Bottle (75cl)\n    ABV 12%\n    Stock Number 31d1144\n    42 left in stock\n\n£31.45\n-\n+\nroll over to zoom\n\nOVERVIEW\n\n    Perhaps the most alluring and iconic Champagne today, Moet Imperial is a treasure of Champagne society.\n\n    Moet & Chandon Impérial was created in 1869 and is the House’s iconic champagne. It is one of the best selling products in the world. The champagne embodies the House’s unique style as it is created from more than 100 different wines using a blend of Pinot Noir, Pinot Meunier and Chardonnay grapes. The grape mixture is responsible for the array of tastes, ranging from brioche and cereal to the customary earthy flavours we associate with Moët Champagne.\n\n    The Moet Imperial is suitable for all occasions. Pair it with what you wish at the dinner table.\n\n    Comes in the manufacturer\'s presentation box.\n\n    Enjoy it on a Aperol Spritz, add 3 parts of Moët & Chandon Brut Impérial Champagne to 2 parts of Aperol\n    Top up with Tonic Water\n\n    and simply add ice and a slice of orange.", "Moët Imperial - NV", "White | France, Champagne | (1.5)L", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "moet-3", "", "", "2015-04-18 21:17:12", "2015-04-18 21:17:12", "", "0", "http://gabaproject.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/moet.jpg", "0", "attachment", "image/jpeg", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("28", "5", "2015-04-15 20:26:28", "2015-04-15 20:26:28", "<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px;\">The NV Imperial is a straightforward, tasty Champagne made in a easygoing style, with good length and a clean, refreshing finish. Anticipated maturity: 2008-2010. Antonio Galloni</span>", "Moët Imperial - NV", "Moet & Chandon was founded in 1973 by Claude Moet, and has grown to be one of the world\'s largest Champagne houses. Moet & Chandon Champagne is made exclusivley from the three champagne grapes, Pinot Noir, Pinot Meunier and Chardonnay. Even though the production is large, Moët is noted for high quality and consistency from year to year. That consistency is the hallmark of the large, Marque Champagne brands. Buy Moet & Chandon online and pickup in-store or ship to select states.", "publish", "open", "open", "", "moet-imperial-nv", "", "", "2015-04-15 23:39:41", "2015-04-15 23:39:41", "", "0", "http://gabaproject.com/product/moet-imperial-nv/", "0", "product", "", "0");
